{"tid":1499190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有無手足有30年前波羅的海同今日香港人鏈對比圖","createTime":"2019-08-23T15:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T15:56:30.000Z","uid":6435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a7f10b63f9b558ce1303da3ddcd528565df732cf","tid":1499190,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:41:52.000Z","msg":"想拎黎擺係TWITTER打文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0325fbfeacd57317f523c89ff7b85c81ac26179","tid":1499190,"uid":169195,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:43:24.000Z","msg":"人地距離幾遠, 你幾遠 ar..."},{"pid":"ec6f3597d9e28fb3346405e4d646ef56076eaa94","tid":1499190,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0325fbfeacd57317f523c89ff7b85c81ac26179","tid":1499190,"uid":169195,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:43:24.000Z","msg":"人地距離幾遠, 你幾遠 ar..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c829491b2ecea3600a7129b28436071507c8c7e2","tid":1499190,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:44:41.000Z","msg":"英國重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍<br />\n<br />\n英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n記得同父母講簽左有咩好處<br />\n點解要簽?<br />\n1.居英權 <br />\n2.去美國唔洗簽證 <br />\n3.英國係法治，非人治 <br />\n4.民主自由 <br />\n5.房屋政策教好 <br />\n6. 去歐美國家入境時唔會被問長問短 <br />\n7. 00後可以用家庭團聚形式入籍 <br />\n8.攞到脫離現有被強加國籍啲條件<br />\n9.英國無再教育營<br />\n10.無2047問題<br />\n11.因為多左英國公民喺香港，英國政府會易D發聲<br />\n12.如取消左被強加國籍，可以喺香港call領事保護及用英國護照入境中國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPostal code 填000000<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6stNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=9ec5a461\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"dc3f8cfd67dada61b2b3773399f38e7762045aa8","tid":1499190,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0325fbfeacd57317f523c89ff7b85c81ac26179","tid":1499190,"uid":169195,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:43:24.000Z","msg":"人地距離幾遠, 你幾遠 ar..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:44:57.000Z","msg":"唔好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89eb1057b14e8294ca6cd8c59cf276c25abbb9f1","tid":1499190,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0325fbfeacd57317f523c89ff7b85c81ac26179","tid":1499190,"uid":169195,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:43:24.000Z","msg":"人地距離幾遠, 你幾遠 ar..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:44:58.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\n物輕情義重呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a61045c83cf9361d6567c9c0aed7bccacdeba1d","tid":1499190,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89eb1057b14e8294ca6cd8c59cf276c25abbb9f1","tid":1499190,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0325fbfeacd57317f523c89ff7b85c81ac26179","tid":1499190,"uid":169195,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:43:24.000Z","msg":"人地距離幾遠, 你幾遠 ar..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:44:58.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\n物輕情義重呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:46:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f5d0a8ecbd509955bbdca442af6615537aaf66","tid":1499190,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b31523fdffa1721c6e5a195548979f6ac72f9fb","tid":1499190,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s